data.description: Escape to your own private retreat! This charming home offers the serenity of a large wooded lot in a quiet area of Gainesville, with the convenience of nearby shopping and dining. With no rental restrictions or HOA, enjoy the freedom to make it your own or make it an investment property now or in the future! Plenty of storage, a wrap-around porch, and a peaceful creek on the property make this home a haven for relaxation and play. Don't miss out - schedule your showing today!
